name: 薙切アリス - Nakiri Alice / Food Wars! LoRa - 食戟のソーマ
description:
24th Release, 薙切アリス - Nakiri Alice From Food Wars! - 食戟のソーマ.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

Character's request, & I wanted one in Good Quality with more Flexibility.

About this Lora:

  • Lora trained on 184+ Images that i sorted manually, at the max quality possible (Original + AnimeSceencaps Art 4K Images, Were used in the datasets) SFW+NFSW.

  • Can do Different Official skins. (Chef, School Uniform, Black Dress, Lab Skin.

  • He can do Original Art & Pratically Anime TV Like Nakiri Alice.

  • Trained at 512x Resolution.

  • NAI Used, Work with Majority of the Anime Model's.

  • Work's greatly with Detail Tweaker Lora. (I Recommend to use it).

For Prompts & Weight:

Flexibility is Good. (See examples images).

About Trigger Words & Prompts: AliceKV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples images.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Best Result 0.8-1.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

PS: If this get enough interest i will probably do: Nakiri Erina, Nakiri Leonara (Mother), & Other Character's.

modelVersions.name: V4
modelVersions.description:
I pruned White hair & Blonde hair & Red Eyes, so normally you don't need to put in prompt, but if they don't appear put: ((White hair, Red Eyes)) prompt.

For Official Default Skin: Sometime the best weights is varying per model's, Work perfectly at Weight 1.

For Flexibility: for like clothes that don't exist put 0.6 - 0.8 Weight, See my Examples images for this.

Officiel Chef Default Skin: Is not precise with button (But easy to fix in PS), Other Skins are very good tho.
